    "en": {
      "title": "The paddy marketing board will buy paddy from tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A kilo of paddy costs Rs. Agriculture Minister Mahinda Amaraweera said that rice will be purchased tomorrow (17th) through the marketing board at a price of 120 rupees, 125 rupees per kilo of samba rice and 130 rupees per kilo of kiri samba rice.",
        "He also said that 2000 million rupees have been set aside for the purchase of paddy this year.",
        "He also mentioned that since paddy harvesting has started, the price of a kilo of paddy in some areas has come down to 90 rupees."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "tomorrow",
          "label": "DATE"
        }
      ],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
        [
          {
